    <item>
      <title>泰国新总理正在审查 140 亿美元现金发放情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/new-thai-prime-minister-scrutinizing-14-billion-cash-handouts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国新任总理帕东丹·西那瓦表示，需要对泰国关键的经济刺激措施 — — 即向公民发放近 140 亿美元现金 — — 进行进一步研究，以确保符合该国的财政纪律法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/new-thai-prime-minister-scrutinizing-14-billion-cash-handouts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 07:35:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其展示实力，在非洲扩大影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/turkey-to-start-oil-drilling-in-somalia-as-it-seeks-bigger-influence-in-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其为扩大在非洲的影响力和加强能源安全，将于下个月派遣长 86 米的“Oruc Reis”号研究船前往索马里海上石油区块进行勘探。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/turkey-to-start-oil-drilling-in-somalia-as-it-seeks-bigger-influence-in-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士农民收成不佳意味着消费者购买的西红柿更便宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/swiss-economy-bad-harvests-for-farmers-mean-cheaper-tomatoes-for-shoppers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于瑞士农民来说，坏消息却是对于支付欧洲最高食品价格的消费者来说的好消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/swiss-economy-bad-harvests-for-farmers-mean-cheaper-tomatoes-for-shoppers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市投资者失去衡量情绪的关键指标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/chinese-stock-investors-lose-a-key-indicator-to-gauge-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国可能在 2024 年出现首次年度股票资金流出 — — 但如果发生这种情况，投资者不会从交易所数据中得知。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/chinese-stock-investors-lose-a-key-indicator-to-gauge-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
